        {
            "title": "歐洲央行執委Cipollone稱全球動盪可能影響歐元區復甦",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據西班牙《國家報》報導，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>執委Piero Cipollone在接受該報採訪時警告，全球動盪可能衝擊歐元區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「不確定性可能會加劇，進而影響經濟復甦的力度，因為它會危及投資，」他對該報表示。「這可能會產生影響，尤其對經濟成長而言，顯然也會影響通膨。若這種不確定性持續存在，將對實體經濟造成衝擊。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲央行自去年6月以來一直沒有降息，鑒於通膨率徘徊在2%的目標附近，投資者和大多數經濟學家預計該行將在整個2026年按兵不動。歐洲央行最新預測顯示，今年歐元區經濟料成長1.2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f0b7e4e4-a445-31b7-b362-2e548d1b8459-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「GDP表現穩健，我們預計實際數據甚至可能優於預期，」 Cipollone表示。「近幾個月來，通膨率一直在我們的目標水平附近波動。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Cipollone負責歐洲央行的數字歐元項目，他重申了這項工作的重要性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「潛在的地緣政治緊張局勢以及任何支付工具的軍事化都會增加風險，這更加凸顯了我們需要一個能夠滿足我們所有支付需求、基於歐洲技術和基礎設施的歐洲支付系統，」他說。「也就是說，一個完全由我們掌控的系統。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB’s Cipollone Says Uncertainty May Increase, Hitting Recovery</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%9F%B7%E5%A7%94cipollone%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%8D%80%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A6-061410505.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 14:48:22",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
