        {
            "title": "中國大使稱「密切」關注澳大利亞在達爾文港問題上的動向",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"713\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gbSLJ2D1C_4xVdtuHAhvag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/84fd5c3247ad0e585bfe6ff97cca9553\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國駐<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澳大利亞;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澳大利亞\">澳大利亞</a>大使表示，北京正在「密切關注」堪培拉如何處理目前租給一家中國公司的港口問題，如有必要中國將介入。澳大利亞工黨政府已承諾將該港口收歸本國控制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國駐澳大利亞大使肖千周三在堪培拉對記者表示，如果該港口通過強制出售予以收回，北京有「義務保護中國企業在海外的合法權益」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"達爾文港攝影師：Darrian Traynor/Getty Images\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8PXTMHr_Y9IVX.GLQA67w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b598ecc5ba90eb9cb21bce976337ed20\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">達爾文港攝影師：Darrian Traynor/Getty Images</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自總理阿爾巴內塞承諾將港口收歸澳大利亞控制，以及其中左翼政府於5月以壓倒性優勢贏得連任以來，該港口的狀態鮮有實質進展。若強行要求出售，可能引發北京方面的強烈反彈。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4b90c7f5-1eaa-3d00-901f-59721264ee1c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們會視情況而定，看何時該表態、採取行動，以體現中國政府的立場，並表明我們保護中國企業合法權益的決心和立場。」肖千在記者會上說，「同時，我希望這個問題能得到妥善處理」，以展現澳大利亞歡迎中國企業的投資。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：5月份，對華關係回暖之際 澳大利亞總理面臨收回戰略港口控制權的政治考驗</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"713\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SLsIZD3eXEsxs2m.qR5X3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/82ed208af026da62d7a1dc1c4131f9bc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Is Watching Australia ‘Very Closely’ on Darwin Port Issue</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ben Westcott.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E7%A8%B1-%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%9C%A8%E9%81%94%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E6%B8%AF%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8B%95%E5%90%91-055022979.html",
